targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  COUNT(distinct cmcd_key_sid)
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)   
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
LIMIT
  50

SELECT
  COUNT(distinct cmcd_key_sid)
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)   
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
LIMIT
  50

SELECT
  request_browser_name,
  COUNT(distinct cmcd_key_sid),
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000    
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')
GROUP BY
  request_browser_name
LIMIT
  50

SELECT
  request_country_name,
  COUNT(distinct cmcd_key_sid),
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000      
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  request_country_name
LIMIT
  50

SELECT
  request_country_code AS metric, -- Uses 2-letter country code
  COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid) AS value
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND request_country_code IS NOT NULL
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000  
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  metric

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(request_datetime, '$time_aggregate') AS time,
  COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid) AS unique_sessions
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000  
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  time
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  request_asn_organization AS ASN,
  COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid) AS sessions,
  AVG(cmcd_key_mtp) AS mean_throughput,
  COUNTIF( (cmcd_key_bs IS TRUE OR cmcd_key_sta = "r" ) AND cmcd_key_su IS NOT TRUE and cmcd_key_ot = "v") AS non_startup_buffer_starvations
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND request_asn_organization IS NOT NULL
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000      
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  ASN
ORDER BY
  sessions DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT
  ANY_VALUE(cmcd_key_cid),
  COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid),
  COUNT(cmcd_key_cid),
  AVG(cmcd_key_msd),
  COUNTIF( (cmcd_key_bs IS TRUE OR cmcd_key_sta = "r") AND cmcd_key_su IS NOT TRUE AND cmcd_key_ot= "v"),
  COUNTIF( (cmcd_key_bs IS TRUE OR cmcd_key_sta = "r") AND cmcd_key_su IS NOT TRUE AND cmcd_key_ot= "v") / COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid),
  AVG(CASE WHEN cmcd_key_sta = "p" THEN cmcd_key_ltc ELSE NULL END),
  AVG(cmcd_key_mtp),
  AVG(cmcd_key_ttfb),
  AVG(cmcd_key_ttlb)
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_cid IS NOT NULL
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  cmcd_key_cid
LIMIT
  50

WITH LatencyData AS (
  SELECT
    cmcd_key_sid,
    cmcd_key_cid,
    cmcd_key_ltc
  FROM
    ${table_name}
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
    AND cmcd_key_sid IS NOT NULL
    AND cmcd_key_cid IS NOT NULL
    AND cmcd_key_ltc IS NOT NULL
    AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
    AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000
    AND (cmcd_key_sta = "p" OR cmcd_key_sta = "s")    
    AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
    AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
    AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
    AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')
),
Percentiles AS (
  SELECT
    cmcd_key_cid,
    -- Calculate approximate percentiles for latency
    APPROX_QUANTILES(cmcd_key_ltc, 100) AS quantiles
  FROM
    LatencyData
  GROUP BY
    cmcd_key_cid
)
SELECT
  p.cmcd_key_cid AS content_id,
  -- Extract specific percentiles from the array
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(25)] AS p25_latency,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(35)] AS p35_latency,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(50)] AS p50_latency,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(75)] AS p75_latency,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(95)] AS p95_latency,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(99)] AS p99_latency,
  -- Calculate other stats
  AVG(ld.cmcd_key_ltc) AS avg_latency,
  STDDEV(ld.cmcd_key_ltc) AS stddev_latency,
  MIN(ld.cmcd_key_ltc) AS min_latency,
  MAX(ld.cmcd_key_ltc) AS max_latency
FROM
  Percentiles p
JOIN
  LatencyData ld ON p.cmcd_key_cid = ld.cmcd_key_cid
GROUP BY
  p.cmcd_key_cid,
  p25_latency,
  p35_latency,
  p50_latency,
  p75_latency,
  p95_latency,
  p99_latency
ORDER BY
  p95_latency DESC

WITH Data AS (
  SELECT
    cmcd_key_cid,
    cmcd_key_msd
  FROM
    ${table_name}
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
    AND cmcd_key_cid IS NOT NULL
    AND cmcd_key_msd IS NOT NULL
    AND cmcd_key_msd < 6000
    AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
    AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000    
    AND (cmcd_key_sta = "p" OR cmcd_key_sta = "s")    
    AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
    AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
    AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
    AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')
),
Percentiles AS (
  SELECT
    cmcd_key_cid,
    -- Calculate approximate percentiles for Media start Delay
    APPROX_QUANTILES(cmcd_key_msd, 100) AS quantiles
  FROM
    Data
  GROUP BY
    cmcd_key_cid
)
SELECT
  p.cmcd_key_cid AS content_id,
  -- Extract specific percentiles from the array
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(25)] AS p25_msd,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(35)] AS p35_msd,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(50)] AS p50_msd,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(75)] AS p75_msd,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(95)] AS p95_msd,
  p.quantiles[OFFSET(99)] AS p99_msd,
  -- Calculate other stats
  AVG(ld.cmcd_key_msd) AS avg_msd,
  STDDEV(ld.cmcd_key_msd) AS stddev_msd,
  MIN(ld.cmcd_key_msd) AS min_msd,
  MAX(ld.cmcd_key_msd) AS max_msd
FROM
  Percentiles p
JOIN
  Data ld ON p.cmcd_key_cid = ld.cmcd_key_cid
GROUP BY
  p.cmcd_key_cid,
  p25_msd,
  p35_msd,
  p50_msd,
  p75_msd,
  p95_msd,
  p99_msd
ORDER BY
  p95_msd DESC

panels.title: Video Bitrate distribution by Content ID

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  ANY_VALUE(cmcd_key_msd)
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_sid IS NOT NULL
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')
GROUP BY
  cmcd_key_sid

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(request_datetime, '$time_aggregate') AS time,
  MIN(cmcd_key_msd) AS min_media_start_delay,
  AVG(cmcd_key_msd) AS avg_media_start_delay,
  MAX(cmcd_key_msd) AS max_media_start_delay 
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  time
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  ANY_VALUE(cmcd_key_url_domain),
  AVG(cmcd_key_ttfb),
  AVG(cmcd_key_ttlb),
  AVG(cmcd_key_mtp),
  COUNTIF( (cmcd_key_bs IS TRUE OR cmcd_key_sta = "r") AND cmcd_key_su IS NOT TRUE AND cmcd_key_ot = "v"),
  COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid)
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_url_domain IS NOT NULL
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0 
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000  
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  cmcd_key_url_domain

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(request_datetime, '$time_aggregate') AS time,
  SAFE_DIVIDE(COUNTIF(cmcd_key_rc >= 200 AND cmcd_key_rc < 300) * 100.0, COUNT(*)) AS HTTP_Success,
  SAFE_DIVIDE(COUNTIF(cmcd_key_rc >= 400 AND cmcd_key_rc < 500) * 100.0, COUNT(*)) AS HTTP_Client_Error,
  SAFE_DIVIDE(COUNTIF(cmcd_key_rc >= 500 AND cmcd_key_rc < 600) * 100.0, COUNT(*)) AS HTTP_Server_Error
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_rc IS NOT NULL
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  time
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(request_datetime, '$time_aggregate') AS time,
  AVG(cmcd_key_ttfb) AS avg_ttfb,
  MIN(cmcd_key_ttfb) AS min_ttfb,
  MAX(cmcd_key_ttfb) AS max_ttfb
FROM
  ${table_name}
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime)
  AND cmcd_key_ttfb IS NOT NULL
  AND cmcd_key_ltc > 0
  AND cmcd_key_ltc < 15000  
  AND ('${cmcd_key_cid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_cid = '${cmcd_key_cid:raw}')
  AND ('${cmcd_key_sid:raw}' = '__all__' OR cmcd_key_sid = '${cmcd_key_sid:raw}')
  AND ('${request_country_code:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_country_code = '${request_country_code:raw}')
  AND ('${request_browser_name:raw}' = '__all__' OR request_browser_name = '${request_browser_name:raw}')  
GROUP BY
  time
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT 
  DISTINCT cmcd_key_cid 
FROM 
  ${table_name} 
WHERE 
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime) -- Filters data based on the Grafana dashboard's time range
  AND cmcd_key_cid IS NOT NULL 
ORDER BY 
  cmcd_key_cid

SELECT 
  DISTINCT cmcd_key_sid 
FROM 
  ${table_name} 
WHERE 
  $__timeFilter(request_datetime) -- Filters data based on the Grafana dashboard's time range
  AND cmcd_key_sid IS NOT NULL 
ORDER BY 
  cmcd_key_sid
SELECT DISTINCT request_country_code FROM ${table_name} WHERE $__timeFilter(request_datetime) AND request_country_code IS NOT NULL ORDER BY request_country_code
SELECT DISTINCT request_browser_name FROM ${table_name} WHERE  $__timeFilter(request_datetime) AND request_browser_name IS NOT NULL ORDER BY request_browser_name
